  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "All that money, the billions and trillions of dollars which have been transferred to the Arab countries without the Arabs having to lift a finger, it was foreign countries who found the oil, foreign countries who brought up to the ground, who distributed it.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Without lifting a finger, they got-- God gave them trillions of dollars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And if that money would be distributed among the 22 Arab states, of the Arab League, they can all live decent lives, have all the hospitals, have all the schools, and all have decent lives.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Whereas many of them still live in abject poverty and-- because of these Arab sheikhs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And America, has to think twice what's going on-- what's going on, the blowing up of the-- of these soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We are placing our hopes in these-- in these errand boys, kings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we see how they hate, not only hate Jews, but hate Christians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It's very fundamental.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there will be fundamentalism in the Muslim states, within Arab states for the next several hundred years, fundamentalism.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And if anybody thinks otherwise, that plane which blew up the other day-- what's the name, the TWA plane that blew up a day or two ago-- that may have been from a bomb placed, or a rocket placed by a radical-- a radical-- a radical from an Arab state.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And America knows it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And if people think, like these Marxist atheists, like Rabin and Peres thought, oh yeah, we'll all sing the-- we'll all thing the-- the-- the-- the-- the-- national, you know, the Communist national together.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We'll all be happy together in a state.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They might think that was the idealism.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The Arabs don't think that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were just using-- going along with Rabin and Peres.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
